        <item>
            <title>英制双层电巴投入服务，九巴：成本贵柴油巴逾半冀能获政府资助</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/11/adlbus/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=adlbus</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/05/11/adlbus/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:01:23 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[亚历山大丹尼士]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电巴]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1235110</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前来自英国巴士制造商亚历山大丹尼士（ADL）的 Enviro500EV 双层电巴通过运输署测试，并获发牌。首辆专为香港设计的全新 Enviro500EV，今日在城巴 112 号线，从长沙湾苏屋邨至北角百福道间运行，吸引了大量巴士迷及市民体验。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413468230-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413468230-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413468230.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>该款电巴在中国大陆组装，主要零件来自欧洲，采用 ADL 电池，这些电巴搭载水冷系统和电池管理系统，并在车顶装设了太阳能薄膜，增强了电池的效能和寿命。电巴充电时间约 2.5 小时，续航力可达 300 公里，足以应对大部分日常路线的需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413306452-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413306452-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413306452.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Enviro500EV 电巴设计亦考虑到乘客的舒适和安全，车内装有仿木地板和大地色系座椅，提供双轮椅泊位、免费 5G WiFi 和 USB 充电插座等设施。与比亚迪电巴相比，ADL 电池的配置令下层可配置更多座位，达到 27 个。</p><p>首次运行的 Enviro500EV 双层电巴吸引大批市民试乘，当中包括不少巴士迷。早上 9 点已有人在长沙湾排队，巴士迷对这次新车的首航表现感到满意，尤其是其平稳的刹车和加速性能，以及比较安静的驾驶环境。九巴已计划将这款电巴投入更多过海路线，进一步扩展其电动车队，实现 2040 年全线转向新能源车的目标。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413394288-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413394288-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413394288.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413407833-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413407833-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413407833.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413424066-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="387" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413424066-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413424066.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 387px" /></p><p>九巴传讯及公共事务部主管简学悕表示，电巴成本较传统柴油巴士高出一半。未来希望能获得政府的资助。早前九巴行政总监（署理）关翠兰曾表示，公司正与政府商讨资助事宜，并强调不会依赖单一车厂，以分散投资风险，但暂未决定 ADL 与比亚迪电巴的比例。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1235114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413477784-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413477784-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/blobid1715413477784.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20240511/s00001/1715412705287/%e8%8b%b1%e8%a3%bd%e9%9b%99%e5%b1%a4%e9%9b%bb%e5%b7%b4%e4%bb%8a%e9%a6%96%e8%bc%89%e5%ae%a2-%e9%80%be%e7%99%be%e3%80%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%a3%ab%e8%bf%b7%e3%80%8d%e7%ad%89%e5%80%99-%e6%88%90%e6%9c%ac%e8%bc%83%e6%9f%b4%e6%b2%b9%e5%b7%b4%e8%b2%b4%e9%80%be%e5%8d%8a-%e4%b9%9d%e5%b7%b4%e7%9b%bc%e7%8d%b2%e6%94%bf%e5%ba%9c%e8%b3%87%e5%8a%a9">明报</a>、<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20231104/s00001/1699028032272/%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A510%E8%BC%9B%E8%8B%B1%E8%A3%BD%E9%9B%99%E5%B1%A4%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%B7%B4%E5%A3%AB-%E5%8F%AF%E8%BC%89%E5%AE%A2127%E4%BA%BA-%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E7%BD%B2%E6%AD%A3%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6">明报</a>、<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/996207/%E7%9B%B4%E6%93%8A%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%8B%B1%E8%A3%BD%E9%9B%99%E5%B1%A4%E9%9B%BB%E5%B7%B4-%E8%BC%89%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F122%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%A8%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E5%86%A0-%E5%B0%87%E8%A1%8C%E9%A7%9B%E9%81%8E%E6%B5%B7%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A">香港 01</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.kmb.hk/news_detail.html?id=908&amp;year=2024">九巴</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/11/adlbus/life-tech/auto/">英制双层电巴投入服务，九巴：成本贵柴油巴逾半冀能获政府资助</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
